---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Custom Scent Candle Creation"
  description="Design your own unique fragrance blend and create personalized candles in Centerville, TN."
  price="$30-40 per person"
  duration="2-2.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="custom candles, fragrance blending, personalized candles, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Custom Scent Candle Creation - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>
      Experience the ultimate in personalization with our Custom Scent Candle Creation service. Design your own signature fragrance that reflects your unique taste, then pour it into beautiful candles you'll treasure forever.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      This premium experience allows you complete creative control. You'll work with our fragrance experts to develop your own unique scent profile, experimenting with different combinations until you create your perfect signature fragrance. Then you'll pour your custom candles with pride knowing they contain your exclusive scent blend.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal fragrance consultation</li>
      <li>Access to 40+ premium fragrance oils</li>
      <li>Unlimited scent blending experiments</li>
      <li>Expert fragrance matching guidance</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax and containers</li>
      <li>Professional pouring instruction</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 candles with your signature scent</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Anyone wanting a truly personalized creation. Perfect for self-care enthusiasts, gift-makers, and those seeking a luxurious, one-of-a-kind experience.
    </p>

    <h3>The Custom Creation Process</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Fragrance preference assessment (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Scent exploration and education (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Custom blend creation and refinement (30-45 minutes)</li>
      <li>Candle pouring with your custom scent (30 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing and wrapping (10 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $30-40 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2-2.5 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-4 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Create your signature scent!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"This was such a special experience! I created my signature scent and now I have beautiful candles that smell uniquely like me!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Sophie T.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The staff was so patient helping me develop my perfect scent. The final candles are absolutely gorgeous!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Lisa M.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Worth every penny! I have custom candles with my own fragrance. It's like wearable scent but for your home!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Victoria K.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Scented Candle Making Experience</h3>
        <p>Blend your own signature scents and create custom scented candles.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/scented-candle-making-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Candle Making Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional candle-making techniques from start to finish.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/candle-making-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Essential Oil Candle Workshop</h3>
        <p>Create luxurious candles using pure essential oils.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/essential-oil-candle-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
